PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776957067
OL,3,CAncient tree which inspired Brambly
OL,4,CHedge cottage discovered in Epping
OL,5,CForest
OL,7,FThe area was a favourite walking and
OL,8,Fsketching spot for the celebrated
OL,9,Fillustrator and author.
OL,11,FJill Barklem's son and daughter
OL,12,Fvisited the tree this week and
OL,13,Fconfirmed that the shape, setting and
OL,14,Fsurrounding landscape fitted their
OL,15,Fmother's initial inspiration for the
OL,16,FCrabapple Cottage.
OL,18,FHer daughter, Lizzie, said:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776957067
OL,3,CAncient tree which inspired Brambly
OL,4,CHedge cottage discovered in Epping
OL,5,CForest
OL,7,F"Our mother spent countless hours
OL,8,Fexploring Epping Forest, sketchbook in
OL,9,Fhand.
OL,11,F"Seeing this tree, and the landscape
OL,12,Faround it, it's easy to recognise how
OL,13,Fit found its way into Brambly Hedge.
OL,15,F"It's incredibly moving to see that
OL,16,Fthe real-life inspiration is still
OL,17,Fhere, thriving as part of this very
OL,18,Fspecial and protected ancient woodland.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
