PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776957067
OL,3,CAncient tree which inspired Brambly
OL,4,CHedge cottage discovered in Epping
OL,5,CForest
OL,7,F"It's a testament to the accuracy of
OL,8,Fher drawings that, nearly 50 years on,
OL,9,Fwe are still able to identify that
OL,10,Fvery tree."
OL,12,FIn the Brambly Hedge books, which
OL,13,Fcentre on a community of mice and
OL,14,Ftheir adventures, the inhabitants of
OL,15,Fthe tree are Mr and Mrs Apple.
OL,26,@rD@KO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
