PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776957067
OL,3,CAncient tree which inspired Brambly
OL,4,CHedge cottage discovered in Epping
OL,5,CForest
OL,7,FMr Apple is the warden of "the Store
OL,8,FPump", who offers practical and
OL,9,Freliable solutions when challenges
OL,10,Farise. Mrs Apple is a cook who uses
OL,11,Fdifferent plants that grow in and
OL,12,Faround the forest to make delicious
OL,13,Fmeals.
OL,15,FSculptures of the pair can be found
OL,16,Fnear the start of the Brambly Hedge-
OL,17,Fthemed trail in Epping Forest which
OL,18,Fwas launched last October.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
