PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1776957067
OL,3,CAncient tree which inspired Brambly
OL,4,CHedge cottage discovered in Epping
OL,5,CForest
OL,7,FJill Barklem, who died in 2017 aged
OL,8,F66, published the seasonal Brambly
OL,9,FHedge series in 1980, which has since
OL,10,Fsold more than seven million copies.
OL,12,FCaroline Haines, chairwoman of the
OL,13,FCity of London Corporation's Epping
OL,14,FForest and Commons Committee, said:
OL,15,F"As custodians of Epping Forest, we
OL,16,Fare immensely proud that such a
OL,17,Fcherished part of children's literary
OL,18,Fheritage can be traced to a living
OL,19,Ftree within the forest.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
